#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.range"
msgstr "# triton.language.range"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:4
msgid "`range` 是一个向上计数的迭代器，类似于 Python 的 `range()` 函数，但是允许传入更多的参数。"
msgstr "`range` is an upward-counting iterator, similar to Python's `range()` function, but allows more parameters to be passed in."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.range(arg1, arg2=None, step=None, num_stages=None, loop_unroll_factor=None, disallow_acc_multi_buffer=False, flatten=False, warp_specialize=False, disable_licm=False, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `int` /`constexpr`| 必需 | 起始值（单参数时作为结束值，从0开始） |\n"
"| `arg2` | `int`/`constexpr` | - | 结束值（不包含在范围内） |\n"
"| `step` | `int` /`constexpr`| `1` | 一个整数，每次迭代的步长增量|\n"
"| `num_stages` | `int` | - | 流水线阶段数（同时执行的迭代数量） |\n"
"| `loop_unroll_factor` | `int` | - | 循环展开因子（<2表示不展开） |\n"
"| `disallow_acc_multi_buffer` | `bool` | `False` | 禁止dot操作累加器的多缓冲优化 |\n"
"| `flatten` | `bool` | `False` | 自动展平嵌套循环为单层循环 |\n"
"| `warp_specialize` | `bool` | `False` | 启用warp专业化（仅Blackwell GPU） |\n"
"| `disable_licm` | `bool` | `False` | 禁用循环不变代码外提优化 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `int` / `constexpr` | Required | Start value (when single parameter, serves as end value, starting from 0) |\n"
"| `arg2` | `int` / `constexpr` | - | End value (exclusive) |\n"
"| `step` | `int` / `constexpr` | `1` | An integer, the step increment for each iteration |\n"
"| `num_stages` | `int` | - | Number of pipeline stages (number of iterations executed concurrently) |\n"
"| `loop_unroll_factor` | `int` | - | Loop unroll factor (<2 means no unrolling) |\n"
"| `disallow_acc_multi_buffer` | `bool` | `False` | Disable multi-buffering optimization for the dot operation accumulator |\n"
"| `flatten` | `bool` | `False` | Automatically flatten nested loops into a single loop |\n"
"| `warp_specialize` | `bool` | `False` | Enable warp specialization (Blackwell GPU only) |\n"
"| `disable_licm` | `bool` | `False` | Disable loop-invariant code motion optimization |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported yet |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:14
msgid "### 2.2 类型支持"
msgstr "### 2.2 Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:16
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:18
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | × | × |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ×|×| × | × | ✓ | × | × | × | × | × |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | × | × |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ×|×| × | × | ✓ | × | × | × | × | × |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:20
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:22
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:24
msgid ""
"Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。\n"
"disallow_acc_multi_buffer, flatten, warp_specialize, disable_licm 相关功能还不全。\n"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation). The functionalities related to disallow_acc_multi_buffer, flatten, warp_specialize, and disable_licm are not yet complete."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:26
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:28
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def basic_examples():\n"
"    # 单参数：0到9\n"
"    for i in tl.range(10):\n"
"        # i = 0, 1, 2, ..., 9\n"
"        pass\n"
"\n"
"    # 双参数：2到9\n"
"    for i in tl.range(2, 10):\n"
"        # i = 2, 3, ..., 9\n"
"        pass\n"
"\n"
"    # 三参数：0到10，步长为2\n"
"    for i in tl.range(0, 10, 2):\n"
"        # i = 0, 2, 4, 6, 8\n"
"        pass\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Iterators/range.md:30
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def advanced_examples():\n"
"    # 使用循环优化参数\n"
"    for i in tl.range(0, 100, num_stages=3, loop_unroll_factor=4):\n"
"        # 流水线阶段数为3，循环展开因子为4\n"
"        pass\n"
"\n"
"    # 嵌套循环展平\n"
"    for i in tl.range(0, 10, flatten=True):\n"
"        for j in tl.range(0, 20, flatten=True):\n"
"            # 两个循环会被自动展平为单层循环\n"
"            pass\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

